title: Urban Trial Freestyle Update 2 and Crack-3DM [VIPER666]
description:
--===VIPER666===--

Crack provided by 3DM. This updates the game to v1.0.2 (25 Oct 2013)


Update v1.0.2 Changelog:
-----------------------

-We have added additional video settings in Main Menu/ Help & Options/ Video. Try with different settings for optimal quality/performance. Please note that this version overrides your previous settings, so you may want to change them to take advantage of your PC performance.

-Xbox 360 pad (or compatible) has been set as primary controller. If you have more than one controller and one of them is Xbox controller, only this one will work. If you want to play with another controller, please unplug the Xbox 360 controller.

-When running the game on laptop with 2 video cards, please make sure that dedicated card is on while running the game. You can switch on your dedicated video card in video card's driver panel. 

1. Extract
2. Use the installer in the Update folder
3. Copy the contents of the Crack folder into your game folder
4. Enjoy

--===VIPER666===--
